+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012mPgHfMRhUWMNPMK5KCP1f","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have the full picture. Let me design the architecture and delegate to Gemini.\n\n**Architecture Design:**\n\n1. **`src/index.ts`** - Main entry point, exports `DocumentStore` class and interfaces\n2. **Data model**: Each branch stores a `Map<docId, Document>` where `Document` has versions array and current content. A snapshot-based branching model where creating a branch deep-clones the parent branch state. Track branch points for three-way merge ancestor resolution.\n3. **Three-way merge**: For each document modified on either side since divergence, do field-by-field comparison at the deepest leaf level using dot-path notation."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":837,"cache_read_input_tokens":20517,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":837},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b2f2ba8f-7693-44e5-a7f5-46232577aa26","uuid":"a703ae92-0b03-47c4-bab7-106e2f379c84"}
